{"data":[{"name":"91:1","price":"Demi matahari dan sinarnya pada pagi hari.","arabic":"وَٱلشَّمۡسِ وَضُحَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6044,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:2","price":"Demi bulan apabila mengiringinya.","arabic":"وَٱلۡقَمَرِ إِذَا تَلَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6045,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:3","price":"Demi siang apabila menampakkannya.","arabic":"وَٱلنَّهَارِ إِذَا جَلَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6046,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:4","price":"Demi malam apabila menutupinya (gelap gulita).","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا يَغۡشَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6047,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:5","price":"Demi langit serta perancangannya (yang menakjubkan).","arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ وَمَا بَنَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6048,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:6","price":"Demi bumi serta penghamparannya.","arabic":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ وَمَا طَحَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6049,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:7","price":"Demi jiwa serta penyempurnaan (ciptaan)nya.","arabic":"وَنَفۡسٖ وَمَا سَوَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6050,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:8","price":"Maka Dia mengilhamkan kepadanya (jalan) kejahatan dan ketakwaannya.","arabic":"فَأَلۡهَمَهَا فُجُورَهَا وَتَقۡوَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6051,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:9","price":"Sungguh beruntung orang yang menyucikannya (jiwa itu).","arabic":"قَدۡ أَفۡلَحَ مَن زَكَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6052,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:10","price":"Dan sungguh rugi orang yang mengotorinya.","arabic":"وَقَدۡ خَابَ مَن دَسَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6053,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:11","price":"(Kaum) Samud telah mendustakan (rasulnya) karena mereka melampaui batas (zalim),","arabic":"كَذَّبَتۡ ثَمُودُ بِطَغۡوَىٰهَآ","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6054,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:12","price":"ketika bangkit orang yang paling celaka di antara mereka.","arabic":"إِذِ ٱنۢبَعَثَ أَشۡقَىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6055,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:13","price":"Lalu Rasul Allah (Saleh) berkata kepada mereka, \"(Biarkanlah) unta betina dari Allah ini dengan minumannya.\"","arabic":"فَقَالَ لَهُمۡ رَسُولُ ٱللَّهِ نَاقَةَ ٱللَّهِ وَسُقۡيَٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6056,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:14","price":"Namun mereka mendustakannya dan menyembelihnya, karena itu Tuhan membinasakan mereka karena dosanya, lalu diratakan-Nya (dengan tanah).","arabic":"فَكَذَّبُوهُ فَعَقَرُوهَا فَدَمۡدَمَ عَلَيۡهِمۡ رَبُّهُم بِذَنۢبِهِمۡ فَسَوَّىٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6057,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"91:15","price":"Dan Dia tidak takut terhadap akibatnya.","arabic":"وَلَا يَخَافُ عُقۡبَٰهَا","category":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams"],"ayahNumber":6058,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"}],"chapter":["91 (Ash-Shams)","Ash-Shams","Surah Ash-Shams","Chapter Ash-Shams","Shams","Surah Shams","Chapter Shams","Ash Shams","Surah Ash Shams","Chapter Ash Shams","Surah 91","Chapter 91","The Sun","الشمس"]}